---
import CalButton from '../../CalButton.astro'
---

<section class='relative overflow-hidden py-24 md:py-32'>
  <!-- Subtle dot grid texture -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute inset-0'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(52,101,109,0.07) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;'>
  </div>

  <!-- Large faded watermark -->
  <div
    class='pointer-events-none absolute -right-6 top-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 select-none overflow-hidden'
    aria-hidden='true'
    style='font-family: var(--font-heading); font-size: clamp(12rem, 26vw, 22rem); color: rgba(52,101,109,0.06); line-height: 1; white-space: nowrap;'>
    SOLUCIÓN
  </div>

  <div class='relative mx-auto max-w-[1280px] px-5'>
    <div class='grid lg:grid-cols-[1fr_1fr] gap-12 lg:gap-16 xl:gap-24 items-start'>

      <!-- ── LEFT: Headline block ─────────────────────────────────── -->
      <div class='lg:sticky lg:top-28'>
        <h2 class='text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.18em] uppercase text-cream mb-8'>
          Contratar un consultor SEO
        </h2>

        <p
          data-animate
          class='font-heading text-h2 font-bold leading-[0.9] tracking-tight text-cream mb-1'>
          Pero se puede solucionar.
        </p>

        <div data-animate class='mt-6 flex items-center'>
          <div class='h-px w-32 bg-gradient-to-r from-cream/5 to-cream/35'></div>
          <div class='h-px w-10 bg-cream/60'></div>
        </div>

        <p
          data-animate
          class='mt-6 max-w-[40ch] text-base text-cream leading-relaxed text-pretty'>
          En la llamada revisamos tu presencia en Google, analizamos a tu competencia y te digo exactamente qué está fallando y qué hay que hacer para que tus clientes te encuentren.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- ── RIGHT: 4-step process ────────────────────────────────── -->
      <div class='flex flex-col'>

        <!-- Step 1 -->
        <div
          data-animate
          class='relative flex gap-6 py-10 border-b border-surface/10'>
          <div class='shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center pt-0.5 w-10'>
            <span class='text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-cream leading-none mb-0.5'>
              Paso
            </span>
            <span
              class='text-h3 leading-none font-bold text-cream tabular-nums font-heading'>
              01
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class='text-base font-bold text-cream mb-3'>
              Reserva tu llamada gratuita
            </p>
            <CalButton
              text='Agenda tu sesión gratuita'
              variant='cream'
              class='text-sm font-bold px-5 py-2.5'
            />
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 2 -->
        <div
          data-animate
          class='relative flex gap-6 py-10 border-b border-surface/10'>
          <div class='shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center pt-0.5 w-10'>
            <span class='text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-cream leading-none mb-0.5'>
              Paso
            </span>
            <span
              class='text-h3 leading-none font-bold text-cream tabular-nums font-heading'>
              02
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class='text-base font-bold text-cream mb-2'>
              Cuéntame tu situación
            </p>
            <p class='text-base text-cream leading-relaxed'>
              Al reservar, indícame la URL de tu web y qué te preocupa. Nada más.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <!-- Step 3 -->
        <div
          data-animate
          class='relative flex gap-6 pt-10'>
          <div class='shrink-0 flex flex-col items-center pt-0.5 w-10'>
            <span class='text-xs font-bold tracking-[0.14em] uppercase text-cream leading-none mb-0.5'>
              Paso
            </span>
            <span
              class='text-h3 leading-none font-bold text-cream tabular-nums font-heading'>
              03
            </span>
          </div>
          <div>
            <p class='text-base font-bold text-cream mb-2'>
              Hablamos 30 min
            </p>
            <p class='text-base text-cream leading-relaxed text-pretty'>
              Reviso tu web en tiempo real, te explico qué está fallando y por qué Google no te muestra.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>